A 12-year-old boy has been arrested after he reportedly stabbed his 19-year-old brother in their Spring Valley residence within Kayole.The two are said to have engaged in a domestic quarrel before the minor grabbed the knife and stabbed his elder brother.The victim was rushed to the nearby Provide Hospital for first aid before being referred to Kenyatta National Hospital where he died while undergoing treatment.Police recovered the knife and are investigating the incident.Elsewhere, a 17-year-old boy stabbed a 24-year-old man in the abdomen during a dispute over a memory card in Dandora estate on Thursday.Enock Mwabishi dies while undergoing treatment.The minor is currently being held by police investigating the matter.